%% Diagram: Page lifecycle with bfcache and analytics hooks
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Active : load
    Active --> Passive : blur (focus loss)
    Passive --> Active : focus
    Active --> Hidden : visibilitychange (hidden)\nflush metrics here
    Passive --> Hidden : visibilitychange (hidden)\nflush metrics here
    Hidden --> Active : visibilitychange (visible)
    Hidden --> Frozen : pagehide (persisted)\nbfcache stores DOM + JS
    Frozen --> Active : pageshow (persisted=true)\nreset CLS / LCP windows
    Hidden --> Terminated : pagehide (persisted=false)\nlast chance for sendBeacon
    Terminated --> [*]

    note right of Frozen
        unload / beforeunload
        prevent bfcache —
        avoid them.
    end note
